00:32:36.320 --> 00:32:38.450
You've got to hit it
harder, and you've

00:32:38.450 --> 00:32:41.135
got to hit it at
the right launch

00:32:41.135 --> 00:32:46.700
angle, the right trajectory,
the right angle off the bat.

00:32:46.700 --> 00:32:49.650
So this is another
data set showing

00:32:49.650 --> 00:32:52.470
a very similar thing,
