00:53:07.068 --> 00:53:08.817
willing to spend or
the actual people they

00:53:08.817 --> 00:53:11.860
have doing the analysis that
produces the better results?

00:53:11.860 --> 00:53:15.240
ANDY ANDRES: Some it's
