00:53:34.320 --> 00:53:36.550
it always seems like they hit
a double and the fielder really

00:53:36.550 --> 00:53:38.360
screwed up, but it wasn't
close enough to really

00:53:38.360 --> 00:53:39.340
be called an error.

00:53:39.340 --> 00:53:40.710
And given what your
chart showed earlier,

00:53:40.710 --> 00:53:42.334
they're basically
the same kind of hit.

00:53:42.334 --> 00:53:44.212
Is that your observation
as a scorer, too?

00:53:44.212 --> 00:53:44.920
ANDY ANDRES: Yes.

00:53:44.920 --> 00:53:47.830
I don't make the
