00:58:19.750 --> 00:58:21.820
I'm curious if you
share a lot of this

00:58:21.820 --> 00:58:25.330
and if they incorporate
it well or not well.

00:58:25.330 --> 00:58:28.672
ANDY ANDRES: The data I
