Now, I'm not the best
web scraper in the world.

00:58:30.630 --> 00:58:32.916
If one of you want to
have a cup of coffee,

00:58:32.916 --> 00:58:34.540
I have a couple web
scraping questions.

00:58:34.540 --> 00:58:38.750
I'd love to-- I have a couple of
