In other words, they
can find these datasets

00:58:48.430 --> 00:58:53.220
to better do whatever
gaming they're designing.

00:58:53.220 --> 00:58:54.070
It's out there.

00:58:54.070 --> 00:58:55.460
And I would agree with you.

00:58:55.460 --> 00:58:58.220
If I were a game
designer, I'd really

00:58:58.220 --> 00:59:00.350
want to model the
